{"tid":1506982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2015年]警員欠交稅金額飆四成　近8年新高","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:48:57.000Z","uid":34409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e006b11964418b0f4a057c4bb069646685ab30fe","tid":1506982,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"保安局本月向立法會提交文件披露，無力償債警務人員的最新統計數字。數字顯示，今年上半年無力償債警員的總數有所下跌，但欠交稅款的宗數、涉及總額有所上升，今年上半年稅局向警員發出48份追稅通知書，<span style=\"color: red;\">有關警員欠交的稅款合共達77萬元，按年飆四成，為近八年新高。</span><br />\n<br />\n今年上半年，稅局向警員發出的追討稅款通知書總數有48宗，是2011年上半年以來的新高。至於在同期，警員欠交的稅款達77萬港元，是近八年以來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，另有46名警員被列為「無力償債」，按年跌了一成，其中逾七成、即33名警員欠債原因涉及「家人和親友的問題」，3名警員涉及賭博欠債。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%A0%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%85%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E9%A3%86%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E8%BF%918%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A8%2585%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%25A3%2586%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25BF%25918%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=3301a100\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A8%2585%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%25A3%2586%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25BF%25918%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&h=56557a5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%A0%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%85%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E9%A3%86%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E8%BF%918%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/</a>"},{"pid":"2185ecbd1d96d7536d3dc251750288c2df2fbf79","tid":1506982,"uid":47239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"成日問人交幾多稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc6ce5a623304d67ec5074bc589588c422c97c2","tid":1506982,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2185ecbd1d96d7536d3dc251750288c2df2fbf79","tid":1506982,"uid":47239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"成日問人交幾多稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"人地理應交得多，不過唔交姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3152561402ddac92c4a44cbd12415f1e728c1194","tid":1506982,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"067590b889af19a565dc80b0bb6ec9ecaed60890","tid":1506982,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"撐政府既人毫無頁獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40640d86db780fa2cb686b13f3dbb109dce662a5","tid":1506982,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"在稅局做的，叫我們發電郵給稅局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntaxinfo@ird.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n致税務局長<br />\n就最近反送中運動中，連日來警務人員日以繼夜的工作，加班OT及各種津貼，應該是2O18/19年度的2倍，因此，本人要求局長對待警務人員跟其他納稅人一致，調整警務人員2019/20年的暫繳稅，以反映他們在2019/20的收入水平。<br />\n<br />\n祝工作順利<br />\n一納税人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>利申：我只係網上見到，credit俾返原作者</strong>"}]}